EHOO INFO TECH LIMITED (Hereinafter called EHOO) provides professional mobile network service which on the basis of some customer information. These basic information including mobile number, IMEI, contacts and so on. In order to protect your legal rights of privacy information, we hereby make statement of information collecting and usage as follows.

1. Personal information
 When you register an account for data backup, it is necessary for you to provide mobile number or IMEI. We would not match the number with the information of any other person you know. The selected backup data should be uploaded to EHOO server to ensure you can get back or restore the information at any time you want.

 2. Data backup and restore
 Data backup and restore of contacts/ SMS/ local software list is an optional feature. Only you choose to accept the service will us provide corresponding service to you. EHOO would take strictly secure measures to ensure data safety and to keep the data from being visited, used or leaked unauthorized through a variety of security techniques. Network traffic cost would be charged by operators during function operating process.

 3. Disclaimer
 EHOO would not make public, edit or disclose any personal information which obtained during the above mentioned processes, except following conditions:
 (1) In accordance with relevant state laws and regulations;
 (2) To protect the rights and interests of you and the public under emergency circumstances;
 (3) To protect trademark, patents and any other legitimate rights of EHOO;
 (4) Other conditions which need to make public, edit or disclose the above information according to the law.

 EHOO does not assume any liability if any force majeure occurs as follows, but we would try our best to protect your rights and interests, as well as a timely notification would be given to you.
 (1) Hacker attack;
 (2) Great impact caused by telecom operator;
 (3) Network, website shut down caused by government control;
 (4) Virus attack;
 (5) Nature disasters and wars, other uncontrollable, unpredictable or unavoidable events.

 Your acceptance of EHOO service indicates that you understand and agree with the above statement, and authorize EHOO to receive, also keep and make backup your personal information.
 EHOO reserves the rights of adjust and modify the statement according to the products development. Any statement change referring to your personal information would be released in the product or on the website, and your acceptance of EHOO service indicates that you agree with the modified statement.

